<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/22061660">电影中的激情戏在剧本中是怎样的？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1005522" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">会有关于体位之类的描述吗？还是只是“此处有激情戏3分钟”这样？</div>


</div>
